func main() {
	a := []int{0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6}
	b := a[0:4]
 
	fmt.Printf("a=%v, len=%d, cap=%d\n", a, len(a), cap(a))
	fmt.Printf("b=%v, len=%d, cap=%d\n", b, len(b), cap(b))
 
	b = append(b, 10, 11, 12)
 
	fmt.Printf("a=%v, len=%d, cap=%d\n", a, len(a), cap(a))
	fmt.Printf("b=%v, len=%d, cap=%d\n", b, len(b), cap(b))
}
